lliurex_guard_short_description: Configure access to websites from classroom
lliurex_guard_description: LliureX Guard allows you to restric or allow access to certain web domains.
Set Default Policy.desc: Set restrictive or permissive default policy
Edit Blacklist.desc: Set forbidden domain lists for a permissive policy
Edit Whitelist.desc: Set allowed domain lists for a restrictive policy
llx-guard.policy.default.description: Accept all domains defined at the white list, and denylaccess to domains defined in black list.
llx-guard.policy.permissive.description: Enables access to any domain, except those specified in black list.
llx-guard.policy.restrictive.description: Restrict access to any domain, except those specified in white list.
llx-guard.default.domains.desc.whitelist: There are those domains that will be accessible when a restrictive policty will be set.
llx-guard.default.domains.desc.blacklist: There are those domains that will be restricted when a permissive policty will be set.

llx-guard.Pages that contains proxies to: Pages that contains proxies to access forbidden sites
llx-guard.Pages that distribute spyware: Pages that distribute spyware and other malware
